    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-content">
                <h1>About KhumaloCraft</h1>
                <p>Welcome to KhumaloCraft, your one-stop destination for unique handcrafted items! We specialize in creating high-quality artisanal products that reflect the rich cultural heritage and craftsmanship of our community.</p>
                <p>At KhumaloCraft, we believe in the power of craftsmanship to tell stories, preserve traditions, and bring joy to everyday life. Each piece in our collection is carefully crafted by skilled artisans using traditional techniques passed down through generations.</p>
                <p>Our mission is to promote traditional craftsmanship, support local artisans, and share the beauty of African artistry with the world. Whether you're looking for a statement piece for your home or a unique gift for a loved one, you'll find something special at KhumaloCraft.</p>
                <p>Founded in 2005, KhumaloCraft has grown from a small workshop to a thriving community of artisans. We work closely with local craftsmen and women to create sustainable opportunities for economic growth and cultural preservation.</p>
                <p>In addition to our online store, we also operate a physical boutique in the heart of our community. Visitors to our boutique can experience the beauty and craftsmanship of our products firsthand, and learn more about the artisans behind each piece.</p>
                <p>Thank you for supporting KhumaloCraft and joining us on our journey to celebrate creativity, culture, and craftsmanship.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
